<plot>This series, originally presented in eight parts, grew from the book "Gardens of the World" by Penelope Hobhouse and Elvin McDonald. Audrey contributed the book's foreword, and hosts the series from the world's most famous gardens in the United States, Japan, Santo Domingo, Italy, Holland, France and England. After Audrey's illness in 1992, Michael York stepped in as host.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?210208</url></doc>
